<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 22:08:53 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列不反对美国和哈马斯就美国人质达成单独协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-not-opposed-to-separate-deal-between-u-s-and-hamas-for-american-hostages/00000190-0404-dd57-abb4-7e4ef7880000</link><description>布林肯在耶路撒冷开会警告内塔尼亚胡：拜登政府人质协议的失败可能导致整个框架崩溃</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 21:34:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-not-opposed-to-separate-deal-between-u-s-and-hamas-for-american-hostages/00000190-0404-dd57-abb4-7e4ef7880000</guid></item><item><title>前总理的妻子利希·拉皮德 (Lihi Lapid) 发现以色列作家在美国面临的严峻新现实</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/lihi-lapid-wife-of-ex-pm-discovers-grim-new-reality-for-israeli-authors-in-america/0000018f-fea3-d5ad-ad8f-feeb80280000</link><description>莉希·拉皮德本应该在美国进行新书巡演，庆祝她的小说《On Her Own》的英文版发行。相反，她正在特拉维夫参加抗议活动，发现现在没有人愿意接待一位以色列作家，甚至连反对派领导人的另一半也不想接待</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 21:21:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/lihi-lapid-wife-of-ex-pm-discovers-grim-new-reality-for-israeli-authors-in-america/0000018f-fea3-d5ad-ad8f-feeb80280000</guid></item><item><title>为什么埃尔多安认为以色列想要征服土耳其</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-erdogan-thinks-israel-wants-to-conquer-turkey/00000190-02b1-d067-adb0-8eb73eb30000</link><description>最近几周，土耳其总统埃尔多安一再指责以色列密谋加沙后接管土耳其腹地，同时赞扬哈马斯是安纳托利亚的“第一道防线”。这是一种古怪的阴谋论，深深植根于埃尔多安的传记、反犹太主义和他当前的政治困境</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 20:32:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-erdogan-thinks-israel-wants-to-conquer-turkey/00000190-02b1-d067-adb0-8eb73eb30000</guid></item><item><title>联合国安理会批准决议呼吁停火、释放人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/un-security-council-approves-resolution-calling-for-cease-fire-hostage-release/00000190-03c4-dd57-abb4-7bce65a90000</link><description>14个国家对该提案投了赞成票，俄罗斯投了弃权票 ■ 内塔尼亚胡政府公开反对该决议的框架</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 20:18:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/un-security-council-approves-resolution-calling-for-cease-fire-hostage-release/00000190-03c4-dd57-abb4-7bce65a90000</guid></item><item><title>真正的反对派会站出来吗：有人试图将以色列从内塔尼亚胡、无休止的战争和孤立中拯救出来吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/is-anyone-trying-to-save-israel-from-netanyahu-isolation-and-endless-war/00000190-0312-de5e-a5ff-2796ae980000</link><description>本尼·甘茨毫不奇怪地离开内塔尼亚胡政府，这不会增强反对派的力量，因为以色列几乎没有名副其实的反对派。这对于结束加沙战争和巴以冲突来说是个坏消息</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 19:27:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/is-anyone-trying-to-save-israel-from-netanyahu-isolation-and-endless-war/00000190-0312-de5e-a5ff-2796ae980000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人对欧洲“亲以色列”极右势力的崛起感到高兴</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-10/ty-article/.highlight/israelis-myopic-rejoicing-over-the-rise-of-europes-pro-israel-far-right/00000190-031d-d5ad-ad93-275d113b0000</link><description>以色列人最好听取欧洲拉比会议主席拉比·平查斯·戈尔德施密特等人物的意见，他在欧盟大选前夕写道，欧洲犹太人“没有好的选择”</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 18:21:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-10/ty-article/.highlight/israelis-myopic-rejoicing-over-the-rise-of-europes-pro-israel-far-right/00000190-031d-d5ad-ad93-275d113b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 248 天：联合国安理会将就支持停战提案的决议进行投票</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-248-un-security-council-to-vote-on-resolution-backing-truce-proposal/00000190-02f5-de5e-a5ff-27f793a90001</link><description>据报道，拜登政府正在讨论与哈马斯达成协议，以防涉及以色列的谈判失败，释放被关押在加沙的五名美国公民 ■ 美国国务卿布林肯自 10 月 7 日以来第八次访问以色列 ■ 联合国安理会将就美国决议进行投票支持拜登提出的停战提案 ■ 一架以色列无人机在黎巴嫩被击落 ■ 战争进入 248 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 17:03:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-248-un-security-council-to-vote-on-resolution-backing-truce-proposal/00000190-02f5-de5e-a5ff-27f793a90001</guid></item><item><title>忘记反犹太复国主义者吧。让我们成为反卡汉主义者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-10/ty-article-opinion/.premium/forget-being-anti-zionists-lets-be-anti-kahanists/00000190-0228-d660-af95-6fbed3e60000</link><description>世界各地校园里关于反犹太复国主义及其与反犹太主义的关系的语义烟花分散了我们需要进行的辩论的注意力。真正的危险是以色列种族主义极右翼力量的不断增长及其对以色列人、巴勒斯坦人和散居海外的犹太人造成的后果</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 16:45:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-10/ty-article-opinion/.premium/forget-being-anti-zionists-lets-be-anti-kahanists/00000190-0228-d660-af95-6fbed3e60000</guid></item><item><title>两名以色列边境警察被控“无缘无故”向巴勒斯坦人投掷手榴弹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/two-border-policemen-charged-with-throwing-grenade-at-palestinian-for-no-reason/00000190-02c8-d5ad-ad93-26c913a00000</link><description>由于警察的行动，这名巴勒斯坦男子的一只眼睛失明了，据称这种行为是“没有任何正当理由”的。尽管行为严重，但仍决定以最高可判处三年监禁的罪名起诉他们</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 16:33:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/two-border-policemen-charged-with-throwing-grenade-at-palestinian-for-no-reason/00000190-02c8-d5ad-ad93-26c913a00000</guid></item><item><title>“带他们回家”：以色列人在希腊酷玩乐队演唱会上即兴高歌</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/bring-them-home-israelis-lead-impromptu-chant-at-coldplay-concert-in-greece/00000190-0299-d660-af95-6fbf283d0000</link><description>以色列军队周六大胆营救四名人质后，参加酷玩乐队雅典演出的以色列人齐声高喊，呼吁释放哈马斯囚禁中的剩余人质</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 16:22:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/bring-them-home-israelis-lead-impromptu-chant-at-coldplay-concert-in-greece/00000190-0299-d660-af95-6fbf283d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列财政部长斯莫特里奇告诉人质家属潜在的交易是“集体自杀”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/israels-finance-minister-tells-hostages-families-potential-deal-is-collective-suicide/00000190-029e-de5e-a5ff-279e3ccb0000</link><description>极右翼部长贝扎雷尔·斯莫特里奇告诉人质家属，以色列将“不遗余力”营救他们的亲人，但强调他不会支持与哈马斯达成任何包括结束战争的协议</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 16:03:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/israels-finance-minister-tells-hostages-families-potential-deal-is-collective-suicide/00000190-029e-de5e-a5ff-279e3ccb0000</guid></item><item><title>“太糟糕了，你回来了”：被释放的以色列青少年人质说她收到了“可怕的、负面的”评论</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/too-bad-you-returned-freed-israeli-hostage-says-shes-received-negative-comments/00000190-0151-da02-a1dc-fd5b38f00000</link><description>阿加姆·戈尔茨坦-阿尔莫格与她的母亲和兄弟一起从卡法阿扎基布兹被绑架到加沙。她说公众不喜欢她描述自己与绑架者的关系，而且“人们无法理解”作为人质的感受</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 15:02:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/too-bad-you-returned-freed-israeli-hostage-says-shes-received-negative-comments/00000190-0151-da02-a1dc-fd5b38f00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列专家称英国报纸对哈马斯性暴力的评论断章取义</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/israeli-experts-say-u-k-newspaper-took-comments-on-hamas-sexual-violence-out-of-context/00000190-023b-dbe3-a1da-133f981a0000</link><description>10 月 7 日，三名积极反对哈马斯强奸和性暴力否认的以色列人在社交媒体上进行了反击，声称他们对一篇有关性别暴力的文章发表的评论被视为“愤世嫉俗的剥削”</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 14:51:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/israeli-experts-say-u-k-newspaper-took-comments-on-hamas-sexual-violence-out-of-context/00000190-023b-dbe3-a1da-133f981a0000</guid></item><item><title>司法部命令总理办公室删除有关萨拉·内塔尼亚胡与人质家属会谈的推文</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/pms-office-ordered-to-remove-tweets-about-sara-netanyahus-talks-with-hostages-families/00000190-023e-d5ad-ad93-267f8e980000</link><description>司法部解释说，这些帖子违反了政策，该政策规定总理的官方账户不应被用来讨论当选领导人配偶的个人活动，除非总理本人也参与其中</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 13:43:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/pms-office-ordered-to-remove-tweets-about-sara-netanyahus-talks-with-hostages-families/00000190-023e-d5ad-ad93-267f8e980000</guid></item><item><title>以色列预计极右翼在欧洲议会的胜利将驳回对加沙战争的批评</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-expects-far-right-gains-in-european-parliament-will-improve-its-standing/00000190-01eb-dd57-abb4-7beb32460000</link><description>绿党的衰弱和极右翼政党（尤其是法国和德国）的重大进展，可能会帮助以色列拒绝有利于巴勒斯坦人的重大措施。以色列希望新任欧盟外长的政策不会对其持批评态度</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 13:39:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-expects-far-right-gains-in-european-parliament-will-improve-its-standing/00000190-01eb-dd57-abb4-7beb32460000</guid></item><item><title>七种芝士蛋糕食谱，让您的五旬节客人眼花缭乱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-06-10/ty-article/the-top-seven-recipes-for-a-sweet-shavuot/0000017f-e722-df5f-a17f-fffe1d5e0000</link><description>如果没有一块不起眼的——或者不那么不起眼的——芝士蛋糕，五旬节餐就不完整。今年有一些甜、酸、咸的食谱值得尝试</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 13:28:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-06-10/ty-article/the-top-seven-recipes-for-a-sweet-shavuot/0000017f-e722-df5f-a17f-fffe1d5e0000</guid></item><item><title>“一名妇女或她的胎儿可能有危险，但她不会去医院”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-woman-or-her-fetus-could-be-in-danger-but-she-wont-go-to-the-hospital/0000018f-e74b-d11f-a5cf-e7cba5b90000</link><description>对于以色列南部的贝都因妇女来说，怀孕会带来许多问题，自 10 月 7 日以来这些问题有增无减。新的分娩准备课程旨在帮助她们更好地为产房做好准备。该倡议背后的女性表示，“知识就是力量”，她强调这并不是为了教导女性成为“好病人”</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 13:08:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-woman-or-her-fetus-could-be-in-danger-but-she-wont-go-to-the-hospital/0000018f-e74b-d11f-a5cf-e7cba5b90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列研究显示，社交媒体巨头在 10 月 7 日之后未能删除虚假内容</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/social-media-giants-fail-to-remove-conspirative-content-after-oct-7-israeli-study-shows/0000018f-fd4a-de5e-a5ef-fdce63770000</link><description>以色列互联网协会声称，Facebook、Instagram、X、YouTube和TikTok没有充分遏制有关哈马斯袭击和加沙战争的阴谋论和虚假信息，并且无视用户的投诉</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 12:51:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/social-media-giants-fail-to-remove-conspirative-content-after-oct-7-israeli-study-shows/0000018f-fd4a-de5e-a5ef-fdce63770000</guid></item><item><title>以色列议会将对内塔尼亚胡推动的豁免法案草案进行投票；勇于反对</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/knesset-to-vote-on-draft-exemption-bill-pushed-by-netanyahu-gallant-to-oppose/00000190-0164-d5ad-ad93-256d30c00000</link><description>上个月，内塔尼亚胡开始推动最初在拉皮德-贝内特政府领导下提交的豁免法案草案，尽管司法部长加利·巴哈拉夫-米亚拉表示反对，称该法案不适合以色列加沙战争的当前现实。</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 10:26:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/knesset-to-vote-on-draft-exemption-bill-pushed-by-netanyahu-gallant-to-oppose/00000190-0164-d5ad-ad93-256d30c00000</guid></item><item><title>柏林犹太以色列餐厅自 10 月 7 日起关门 20 年后即将关门</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/closed-since-october-7-berlins-kosher-israeli-restaurant-is-folding-after-20-years/00000190-0172-dbe3-a1da-11778efb0000</link><description>Bleibergs 的老板表示，他最终决定永久关闭餐厅，部分原因是人们“在柏林看起来像一个虔诚的犹太人，感觉不舒服”</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 10:15:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/closed-since-october-7-berlins-kosher-israeli-restaurant-is-folding-after-20-years/00000190-0172-dbe3-a1da-11778efb0000</guid></item></channel></rss>